###
### Clojure
###

###
### Initialize

is_formula_installed && return || formula_init

###
### Dependencies

. $Q/java

###
### Installation

wget $CLOJURE_URL
unzip $CLOJURE_FILENAME
echo "java -cp $QUICKNESS_SRC/$CLOJURE_DIRNAME/ clojure.main" > $QUICKNESS_BIN/clj
chmod 755 $QUICKNESS_BIN/clj

###
### Teardown

formula_teardown
